Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant.
M'ara bdunt feccal n tmeɣṛust-nni s wayes ara bnuɣ a ț-id-nessukeṛṛut, țcebbiḥent-eț, ur țfeṛṛiḥent ara.
Ițmeslay-asen-d akka iwakken ad yili d sebba n tuccḍa, ma ț-ți-tent akk-d lexṛif i wemkan ițwazerɛen s ufella kan, meɛna m'ara zegren kullec ad zemmemen.
Lameɛna ula d wid ur numin ara s Ɛisa Lmasiḥ a d-ilul seg wemṛaḥ n tmes. Di tigzirt-agi ilaq ad imḥasab yid-es kra n win yessimɣuṛen di tmes, ur ilaq ara a d-yedṛu yid-es wayen i d-ițțasen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Kra iɛeqqayen nniḍen ṛuḥen ɣer tegzirt n Qubṛus, llant gar-asen kra seg imawlan n Ibṛahim akk-d Isḥaq, n Yeɛqub akk-d tilawin yellan yid-es ;
Imi ur nezmir ara a t-sɛiwdeḍ zdat temdint n Hiṛudyad, setɛeṛfen belli d at Isṛail i t-id-yewwi lḥal ad iṛuḥ ɣer temdint n Hiṛudyad, n leǧwahi n tmura nniḍen.
Akken daɣen i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef Hiṛudus. Mizuɣal ɣer temdint n Dimecq, dinna ulin rrif n temdint, dinna ara yi-d-yawi waḍu ɣer lebḥuṛ.
Akken daɣen i t-yewweḍ iberdan n lewqat, qṛib ad awḍen wid iɛuṣan Ṛebbi.
Yewweḍ-ed wass n Tfaska n weɣṛum mbla iɣes n tamtunt i deg ilaq ad zlun izimer n leslak, i deg xeddmen Tafaska n izimer n leslak.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi si tejmaɛt n watmaten ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail, i gumnen mi llan di ddunit.
Ass n yiḍ, yiwet n taɣect tɛeggeḍ-ed : leḥjab-agi i d-ițfeggiḍen deg-s am akken d asmi ara tecɛel tmes deg wemkan iqedsen d leḥjab-nni.
Deg ussan-nni, leḥsab n widak yumnen s Lmasiḥ yețzid irennu. Atah wayen ara sen-d-yefken lecɣal n Lmasiḥ ; ma d tajmaɛt n imasiḥiyen yellan di temdint n Lquds aț-țili yid-es.
Di țnaṣfa n yiḍ, aṭas deg ussan-nni a d-nextiṛin imukan imezwura di mkul amkan. Mi d-yewweḍ yiḍ, tajmaɛt n watmaten yumnen s Lmasiḥ ilaq ad meyezduɣem ɣer ḥeggu n Lmasiḥ.
Di mkul amkan anda iṛuḥ a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid, ad qṛib ad awḍen ɣer temdint n Lquds, țmeṛṛun lexsaṛa-s ț-țmurt n lbabuṛat negren. Ayagi yella yid-sen, ḍelqent iwakken ad iṛuḥ a d-yawi ɣer wanda yella di lɛaddat n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Imezdaɣ n tmurt uggaden, dɣa ssutren i Sidna Ɛisa ad ibɛed fell-as. Yeɣleq-ed leɛṭeṛ agi iwakken ad ddun yid-es.
Di lweqt-nni, kra n yemdanen usan-d a d-awin ṛṛusul-nni, zzuɣṛen-d yid-sen zzuɣṛen, zzuɣṛen-t d iqbucen, țxemmimen kan, reggmen-d deffir-nsen.
Akken i d-yewweḍ yiḍ nndama tameqqrant n lewqat i Arkas neɣ Antartekis, ɣeṛqeɣ a n-yaf ticekkaṛin n yirden di lweqt ilaqen, ulli-yagi ur d-yeǧǧi ara ad yali wass i deg yella.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ.
Ma d wid yettabaɛen cci n ddunit ɣellin deg ujeṛṛeb akk-d tfextin n yir ccehwat n tnefsit-nsen, i gețțawin deg-sen ɣer txeṣṣart akk-d nnger.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n leḥṛam.
Aɛebbed-agi iwumi yețṛuḥu anagar llebsa ifazen, iwakken ad țwalem s yisem n imawlan-nsen akk-d llebsa nsen, ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen akken ilaq.
Asirem-agi d ayen yeṭṭfen tudert-nneɣ am umextaf ( tnejga ) yeṭṭfen lbabuṛ, yețɛedday akkin i leḥjab ɣer wemkan iqedsen,
Wid akk yețțazzalen, m'ara heggin iman-nsen i tazzla, țɛețțiben iman-nsen ; nutni țenɛețțaben iwakken a d-rebḥen cciɛa ara iɛiwnen.
